FBIS4-62459 "drsov094_p_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-094 Daily Report 13 May 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Trade Minister Arrested After Caught Accepting Bribe Trade Minister Arrested After Caught Accepting Bribe LD1405033194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 2300 GMT 13 May 94 LD1405033194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Armenian Trade Minister Eduardi Grigoryan has been arrested in his office by Ministry of the Interior staff. He was caught red-handed receiving a bribe of $2,500.
